Package com.ftjace.commandapi.Execution

Class CNode

java.lang.Object
com.ftjace.commandapi.Execution.CNode
public class CNode extends Object
Command node class, absolutely necessary if you plan to use the API as intended. Allows for chaining command execution, tab completion, and sub commands.
